{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"8872-i-am-not-afraid","title":"Je n'ai pas peur !","description":"Une petite fille sort seule dans l'obscurité. Que va-t-elle trouver ?\r\nCe livre est l'un des quatre ouvrages de la série 'Grandir'.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Cyrille Largillier"],"illustrators":["Rayika Sen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/8872-i-am-not-afraid"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705396/size3/184db2e732a8ca7d0d9383e42d4f043d.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705396/size6/184db2e732a8ca7d0d9383e42d4f043d.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11677/size6/374d792a22f02961334325d31e5b9e0a.jpg","text":"Je suis une grande fille. Je sors de la maison toute seule.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11678/size6/c8206278f462bef78271753f2e9d630f.jpg","text":"Il fait si sombre ! Y a-t-il quelqu'un ? Qui est là ?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11679/size6/1e74e244a70f7fe3c14d083e05a6f57b.jpg","text":"Oh,  c'est seulement le chat. Je n'ai pas peur.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11680/size6/c727077af70efa2a5d5b9a8378671b16.jpg","text":"Je vois une grande chose sombre dehors ! Qu'est-ce que c'est ?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11681/size6/d308d12c38b62680a573614bcf172480.jpg","text":"Oh, c'est seulement le puits. Je n'ai pas peur.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11682/size6/059ea834e1b1b9d11aecc9e24e5d32fc.jpg","text":"Et ce bruit ! Cric, Cric, cric ! Qu'est-ce que c'est ?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11683/size6/9fe66565ad4ad6b0ade3f8477d236c2f.jpg","text":"C'est seulement ma sœur qui puise l'eau du puits ! Je n'ai pas peur.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11684/size6/5f3d993066bb9fc2b2a5616eccaef355.jpg","text":"J'entends des pas ! Qui est-ce ? Qui est-ce ?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11685/size6/bb60b60314441faaee3f1d6692814302.jpg","text":"C'est ma mère. Elle est revenue des champs.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11686/size6/4cf48d4d82fde38991fcad1607af1c72.jpg","text":"Je suis une grande fille maintenant.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/11687/size6/7834412c7b54d573f69e38c5c9ea5b8a.jpg","text":"Je n'ai peur de rien !","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":111}}